Awww, we all know what mine is 😈

I have a black "beard" 😹 does it make me look like a boy? My human says it's just very cute ❤️

We have different eyes: yellow and green 💛💚🐾🐾✌️❤️🌺

I have my forehead heart.. I guess that's something. 😹 Your little third eye is super cute 😺❤
My baby Mookie has the same thing and he is very healthy as well!
Awww! Luna is partially deaf from a surgery, and Pico is missing a tear duct, so he “cries” a lot. Both are completely unbothered. 😸
Happy Whisker Wednesday sweetie, you are adorable! 😻💗
Interesting! Misha’s tail has a permanent bend, it takes a quirky little turn almost at the very end of his tail😺 #quirks
Awww that makes you even more special ♥️♥️

У нашего кота кончик хвоста хрящик слегка загнут он таким родился 😊
Such a beautiful picture of you. I never noticed the third eyelid before on your pictures. 😻😻
@yuna_leia i looked back and now saw it. It is not an ‘eyecatcher’ (sorry for the word, couldn’t Find another).

You are so beautiful! I have some quirks due to my chromosomal abnornality! My jaw is crooked, I was born with no bottom incisor teeth, I have HUGE eyes and my back legs have had surgery for deformities - totes gives me a schmexy swagger though!😎
Oh, and Baby Stu only has half a tail! He was found in a car engine at only 5 weeks old and his tail was so damaged half of it had to be amputated!🙈🙈🙈
Hmm.... weird quirks... I mean I guess I have an extra floofy tail??? Does that count??
Hahaha!! Cool quirk 😘😘😘 I have one black whisker. All the rest is completely white. 🖤😀

Odin has one "good" eye and the other really is just a useless ball of scar tissue now. But it makes playing hide and seek with him really adorable. He'll hide behind a wall thinking "ok I can't see Mom, so she can't see me." But really his blind side is sticking out.
Omg I have the same thing happen to me too! 😹 I had a mild eye infection for a while when i first got adopted, so my third eyelid likes to peep 😳✨✨
Looking absolutely stunning ! Such a purrfect picture of you honey 💕❤💕❤🙌😽😻
Mira has a third eyelid too. She is very healthy. Sometimes it looks a bit weird🙄you are beautiful and unique ❤️❤️
Oh wooow we Heizöls have seen that! This makes you very unique and even more beautiful ❤️❤️
